article:
'Vischer' may refer to:
* Vischer family of Nuremberg, a family of sculptors active in Nuremberg between
  1453 and 1549
* Wilhelm Vischer (1895-1988), a Swiss pastor, theologian, Hebraist, Old
  Testament scholar and amateur Lied lyricist
* Wilhelm Vischer (botanist) (1890-1960), a botanist
